pageContext.claim: “She [Kristen Welker] still did a relatively fair job, she said, 'Why did you say that?' It's like, why, like, why the hell did you say that? What the hell is wrong? I'm protecting you all night, and now you end the debate.”
pageContext.analysis: This alleged exchange never took place in the second presidential debate. As a professional journalist moderating a debate, NBC's Kristen Welker would not be on the side of either candidate.
